{"word":"G2132 - εὐνοέω - eunoéō - yoo-no-eh'-o - Agree","slug":"G2132","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐνοέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eunoéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-no-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Agree"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>εὐνόεω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Eunoeo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>yoo-no-eh'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to wish (one) well </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to be well disposed, of a peaceable spirit </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from a compound of <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 20:11,6 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>; to <i>be well minded</i> that is <b><i>reconcile</i></b>: - agree."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283\">G5283</a>"}]}